oner.", "- Det er opp til barnehagens leder \u00e5 avgj\u00f8re om det er forsvarlig \u00e5 holde \u00e5pent, sier Baggerud.", "LES OGS\u00c5: V\u00e6rt t\u00e5kefast? Du f\u00e5r antagelig ingenting", "LES OGS\u00c5: - Vi krysser fingrene for at vi slipper t\u00e5ke i dag"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b8b8a4fb6b8dfa281b1da357a928271164298cfb9d19fcde0bdb17fd6bef80e7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-24T19:08:26.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Barnehagens ansatte ble t\u00e5kefaste p\u00e5 Gardermoen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article11674136.ece/cedn9h/ALTERNATES/w980-default/V%C3%A6rnes%20t%C3%A5ke%2011101512121.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e26a87c3ba71a06e7d9e8ee567bb6583e4faa38b.jpg?5984dc6b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Barnehage stengt etter t\u00e5keforsinkelser -adressa.no", "Stengt av sikkerhetsgrunner", "- Opp til leder \u00e5 avgj\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "e26a87c3ba71a06e7d9e8ee567bb6583e4faa38b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Trondheim", "Hallset"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Trondheim,Hallset"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["stengt", "holde \u00e5pent", "barnehagens ansatte", "barnehage stengt", "s\u00f8ndag kveld", "barnehage"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["hallset", "adresseavisen", "gardermoen", "anne-karin baggerud"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["v\u00e6rnes", "polen", "trondheim", "oslo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "ingrun bye sommerstad"}, {"field": "kw-taxon